# ROBOTS

Travis Jeffery and Victor Savkin's Clojure experiment.

### RULES:

- There is one main Robot â€” the robot who began the game
- The Client ignores incorrectly formatted messages

### OPERATIONS

- Move, shoot, rotate

#### SHOOTING

- Shooting will kill 1 robot in same location
- After shooting the robot then stays there, if the robot shoots in same
  direction again that bullet will go into the same dead robot